CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Through its direct relationships with FDIC-insured bank partners, Chime delivers easy-to-use products that address the most critical financial needs of everyday people - spending, saving, accessing liquidity, and building credit, all while avoiding punitive fees. Through our broad suite of products, we have built trusted relationships with 8.6 million Active Members, with 67% of them relying on Chime to serve as their primary financial relationship.
